{"tid":1683234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除非殺晒香港人 否則有香港人就有抗爭","createTime":"2019-10-30T14:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:20:54.000Z","uid":105976,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"affc9e82ee5c14d1e2324234a7a761cc9af2a89e","tid":1683234,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"只有達到五大訴求 雙普選 抗爭先會完結<br />\n<br />\n每一條街 每一個周末 每晚 每一塊牆<br />\n每一個已知同未知既戰場<br />\n都係會變成我地抗爭既場地<br />\n<br />\n民主自由既信念係無法忘記<br />\n<br />\n除非鏟平所有路 拆晒所有牆 殺晒所有香港人<br />\n否則  為左公義 為左家園 為左所愛之人<br />\n抗爭係唔會完<br />\n<br />\n有人話就黎完  我話而家先岩岩開始"},{"pid":"e6ca31d2e5f846540538dd5d5a01684eb4383ff4","tid":1683234,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"a7dbdece79a21c7e47303a66f6f22a3279ffd7f7","tid":1683234,"uid":10258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"無錯，大家堅持落去，留有用之軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續抗爭"},{"pid":"df739a4bf31769e1b9cd8d4a813030d70d694dd6","tid":1683234,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c90ad4848a2806178ecdceb3e921496234c45d","tid":1683234,"uid":141270,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"純粹問個問題<br />\n俾人拉咗嘅果d會再出黎？<br />\n唔會嘅話點樣得出有香港人就會有抗爭？<br />\n唔好成日覺得我地人多<br />\n唔好覺得因為人多就無所謂<br />\n敗北條件好明確<br />\n拉過曬所有肯出黎 願意出黎嘅人<br />\n所以要更加好規劃每一次行動 唔可以白白犧牲手足"},{"pid":"f36f5ebb748ea9067e52960541e6aab6158a9b87","tid":1683234,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2009de1c0f5e1e7a218815d6ff8e061190fa9c","tid":1683234,"uid":218313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6